snippet.title: The Thaumaturge | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add The Thaumaturge to your wishlist and don’t miss any future updates:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1684350/The_Thaumaturge/

We’re finally able to unveil the mystery surrounding our latest project known until this moment under the codename "Vitriol". The Thaumaturge developed by Fool’s Theory and published by 11 bit studios is a story-driven RPG with morally ambiguous choices, exploring the dark and esoteric side of reality in the culturally diverse world of early 20th century Warsaw.

Follow The Thaumaturge:
📕https://discord.gg/11bitstudios
📕https://twitter.com/thaumaturgegame
📕https://www.facebook.com/thaumaturgegame
